objectList.description:
I’m A Single Professionals

At this life stage, it is important to protect your earning ability against Critical Illness (e.g. cancer) and Occupational Disability.


Life Protection is necessary if you are supporting a family. A Hospital Plan helps cover high medical costs. Long-Term Care (ElderShield Supplement) is strongly recommended if you are aged 40 and above.
objectList.name: I’m a single professional

objectList.description:
I’m Married With No Kids

At this life stage, it is important to protect your earning ability against Critical Illness (e.g. cancer) and Occupational Disability.


Life Protection is necessary if you are supporting a family. A Hospital Plan helps cover high medical costs. Long-Term Care (ElderShield Supplement) is strongly recommended if you are aged 40 and above.
objectList.name: I’m married with no kids

objectList.description:
I’m A Parent

At this life stage, it is important to protect your earning ability against Critical Illness (e.g. cancer) and Occupational Disability.


Life Protection is necessary if you are supporting a family. A Hospital Plan helps cover high medical costs. Long-Term Care (ElderShield Supplement) is strongly recommended if you are aged 40 and above.
objectList.name: I’m a parent

objectList.description:
I’m A Student

At this life stage, a Hospital Plan is a priority to help cover high medical costs. Eventually when you enter the workforce, you should also consider Life Protection and protect against Critical Illness and Occupational Disability.
objectList.name: I’m a student

objectList.description:
I’m A Retiree / Pre-Retiree

At this life stage, it is essential to have a good Hospital Plan to help cover high medical costs. Long-Term Care (Eldershield Supplement) is also necessary to cover high costs of caregiving for the future.
objectList.name: I’m a pre-retiree / retiree

objectList.description:
I’m A Homemaker

As your family depends on you to run the household, it is important for you to consider Life Protection, Hospital Plans and protect against Critical Illness. Long-Term Care (ElderShield Supplement) is strongly recommended if you are aged 40 and above.
objectList.name: I’m a homemaker
